item.title: CVE-2023-2320|2024-08-02T06:19:14.813Z -- unknown -- cf7%20google%20sheets%20connector
item.description: The CF7 Google Sheets Connector WordPress plugin before 5.0.2, cf7-google-sheets-connector-pro WordPress plugin through 5.0.2 does not escape a parameter before outputting it back in an attribute, leading to a Reflected Cross-Site Scripting which could be used against high privilege users such as admin
